Package com.mway.bluerange.android.sdk.core.scanning.messages

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BeaconMessageGenerator
    The beacon message generator is used to filter and generate BeaconMessage objects out of Beacon objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AssetTrackingMessageV1
    AssetTracking messages are broadcasted by Relution SmartAssets.
    AssetTrackingMessageV1Generator
    A message generator parsing AssetTrackingMessageV1 messages.
    BeaconJoinMeMessage
    Beacon join me messages are send by BlueRange SmartBeacons, whenever a beacon is able to connect with another one.
    BeaconJoinMeMessageGenerator
    A generator for the beacon join me messages.
    BeaconMessage
    The base class of all beacon messages.
    EddystoneMessage
    Abstract base class of all Eddystone messages.
    EddystoneMessageGenerator  
    EddystoneUidMessage
    Represents an Eddystone UID message containing a Namespace UID and an instance identifier.
    EddystoneUidMessageGenerator
    The beacon message generator class for Eddystone UID messages.
    EddystoneUrlMessage
    Represents an Eddystone URL message.
    EddystoneUrlMessageGenerator
    The beacon message generator class for Eddystone URL messages.
    IBeacon
    An iBeacon is a triple containing a UUID, a major and a minor identifier.
    IBeaconMessage
    Implementation of Apple's IBeacon Bluetooth Low Energy messages.
    IBeaconMessageGenerator
    A message generator for iBeacon messages.
    NullBeaconMessage
    NullObject for BeaconMessage
    RelutionTagMessage  
    RelutionTagMessageGenerator  
    RelutionTagMessageGeneratorV1
    A message generator for Relution Tag messages.
    RelutionTagMessageV1
    A Relution Tag message is a Relution specific advertising message that can be delivered by BlueRange SmartBeacons.
